  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy on quality of vision and dry eye signs
      and symptoms in patients undergoing cataract surgery using the ReZoom® multifocal IOL.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
